snippet.title: Orange Island - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
KICKSTARTER LIVE RIGHT NOW!! ▶ https://bit.ly/orange-island

SUBSCRIBE ▶ https://bit.ly/2rQCKJ2

Orange Island is an upcoming authentic 8-bit action-adventure game with heart. Explore a pastel-hued island while uncovering mysteries from the past. Developed by Ted Sterchi.

Join our mailing list on our website for monthly newsletters with exclusive goodies!
